text: Dichostates trilineatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Hintz in 1912. It is known from Kenya, the Democratic Republic of the Congo, Somalia, Uganda, and Tanzania.BioLib.cz - Dichostates trilineatus.
